WEBVTT

01:32.039 --> 01:34.950
[How dare you!?]

01:35.009 --> 01:40.020
[Episode 20]

01:48.789 --> 01:50.050
There's still someone

01:52.280 --> 01:53.810
waiting for me to come back.

02:22.670 --> 02:23.670
♪ Tell me ♪

02:24.320 --> 02:27.829
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

02:29.390 --> 02:30.540
♪ Walk past me ♪

02:30.840 --> 02:34.670
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

02:35.930 --> 02:38.460
♪ Don't watch me as the rain falls ♪

02:39.260 --> 02:42.020
♪ Love burns too hot as it passes ♪

02:42.829 --> 02:48.579
♪ Even a lifetime of war
cannot be extinguished ♪

02:49.610 --> 02:50.740
♪ Blame me ♪

02:51.390 --> 02:54.890
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

02:56.540 --> 02:57.560
♪ Hide me ♪

02:58.079 --> 03:02.090
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

03:03.410 --> 03:05.900
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

03:06.690 --> 03:09.290
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

03:10.210 --> 03:13.200
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

03:13.220 --> 03:15.390
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

03:15.770 --> 03:18.230
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

03:18.280 --> 03:20.040
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

03:20.070 --> 03:22.540
♪ I never yielded ♪

03:22.900 --> 03:24.340
♪ But why ♪

03:24.630 --> 03:29.130
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

03:29.530 --> 03:31.900
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

03:31.940 --> 03:33.790
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

03:33.820 --> 03:36.200
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

03:36.560 --> 03:38.320
♪ The first time I met you ♪

03:38.310 --> 03:39.440
Now,

03:38.690 --> 03:47.630
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

03:41.280 --> 03:42.930
I really won't make it back.

04:01.620 --> 04:02.730
♪ Blame me ♪

04:03.350 --> 04:06.850
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

04:05.240 --> 04:06.840
I know you want to protect me,

04:07.570 --> 04:08.800
but I don't want to be protected by you—

04:08.500 --> 04:09.560
♪ Hide me ♪

04:09.560 --> 04:10.030
because

04:10.040 --> 04:14.050
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

04:10.650 --> 04:11.910
I want to stand with you

04:13.060 --> 04:14.320
and fight by your side.

04:15.370 --> 04:17.790
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

04:16.829 --> 04:18.700
We're in the same boat to begin with.

04:18.649 --> 04:21.269
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

04:18.750 --> 04:21.950
I'll stand by you
and help you through this to the very end.

04:22.170 --> 04:25.160
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

04:25.180 --> 04:27.300
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

04:27.680 --> 04:30.170
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

04:30.220 --> 04:31.980
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

04:32.010 --> 04:34.530
♪ I never yielded ♪

04:34.840 --> 04:36.360
♪ But why ♪

04:36.570 --> 04:41.110
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

04:41.470 --> 04:43.830
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

04:43.880 --> 04:45.730
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

04:45.760 --> 04:48.090
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

04:48.560 --> 04:50.260
♪ The first time I met you ♪

04:50.680 --> 04:53.780
♪ There was once light ♪

04:54.390 --> 05:02.740
♪ In my soul ♪

05:08.840 --> 05:11.330
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

05:11.380 --> 05:13.140
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

05:11.460 --> 05:12.920
Watch out, Your Highness!

05:13.170 --> 05:15.640
♪ I never yielded ♪

05:15.750 --> 05:16.720
Wanyin...

05:16.000 --> 05:17.520
♪ But why ♪

05:17.730 --> 05:22.300
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

05:22.630 --> 05:24.990
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

05:25.040 --> 05:26.890
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

05:26.920 --> 05:29.240
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

05:29.720 --> 05:31.420
♪ The first time I met you ♪

05:31.840 --> 05:39.880
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

05:42.280 --> 05:43.740
Your Highness, watch out!

05:46.890 --> 05:47.800
Xiahou Dan,

05:49.040 --> 05:49.700
wait for me.

06:30.560 --> 06:31.290
You're here.

06:32.440 --> 06:34.930
♪ In the time and space of chaos ♪

06:35.740 --> 06:38.760
♪ Every time I open my eyes ♪

06:38.870 --> 06:39.480
I'm here.

06:39.470 --> 06:42.670
♪ Your silhouette is engraved inside ♪

06:45.850 --> 06:48.590
♪ Then we transform ♪

06:49.230 --> 06:52.290
♪ Into the blazing light to guard ♪

06:52.659 --> 06:53.640
You're hurt.

06:52.670 --> 06:57.300
♪ Our eternal galaxy ♪

06:56.190 --> 06:56.990
It's nothing.

06:58.170 --> 06:59.090
Just a minor injury.

06:58.170 --> 07:00.670
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

07:01.330 --> 07:04.020
♪ And let time freeze ♪

07:02.120 --> 07:03.850
Let's stop the bleeding first.

07:04.720 --> 07:10.450
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

07:10.840 --> 07:12.080
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

07:12.750 --> 07:15.610
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

07:16.170 --> 07:17.790
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

07:17.820 --> 07:23.840
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

07:24.130 --> 07:25.040
Don't worry.

07:24.300 --> 07:25.790
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

07:26.260 --> 07:29.170
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

07:26.620 --> 07:27.750
I'm not going to die.

07:29.640 --> 07:31.780
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

07:31.760 --> 07:33.470
I haven't helped you
fulfill your wish yet.

07:31.880 --> 07:33.409
♪ We can dance together ♪

07:33.430 --> 07:41.290
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

07:51.480 --> 07:52.740
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

07:53.360 --> 07:56.100
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

07:56.790 --> 07:58.300
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

07:58.360 --> 08:04.290
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

08:02.830 --> 08:03.950
You bastard!

08:04.560 --> 08:05.240
You monster!

08:04.930 --> 08:06.540
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

08:05.700 --> 08:06.430
Get in there!

08:06.830 --> 08:09.790
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

08:07.190 --> 08:07.670
Kneel!

08:09.240 --> 08:09.680
Dan.

08:10.290 --> 08:12.330
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

08:12.410 --> 08:13.940
♪ We can dance together ♪

08:13.970 --> 08:21.830
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

08:18.800 --> 08:21.440
You Great Xia people are truly shameless.

08:21.830 --> 08:23.140
What trash!

08:25.600 --> 08:27.160
If it weren't for the fact that
Dan wants you alive,

08:27.160 --> 08:28.680
I'd have killed you long ago.

08:28.680 --> 08:30.070
Do you think you'd still be here
cursing at us?

08:30.070 --> 08:30.900
Kill me then!

08:31.160 --> 08:32.000
Kill me!

08:33.630 --> 08:34.120
Shut up!

08:35.200 --> 08:35.659
Dan.

08:35.840 --> 08:36.390
Hayuanwang.

08:36.390 --> 08:37.320
Are you alright?

08:39.840 --> 08:40.669
I'm okay, Mr. Bei.

08:40.669 --> 08:41.309
Haqina.

08:41.600 --> 08:42.320
Haqina!

08:43.480 --> 08:44.200
Haqina.

08:44.360 --> 08:45.620
Hang in there, Haqina!

08:47.390 --> 08:48.670
Prince Tu'er.

08:48.910 --> 08:50.820
I... I stabbed him.

08:51.480 --> 08:52.000
Haqina.

08:53.630 --> 08:54.630
I'll kill you all!

08:54.960 --> 08:56.160
I'll kill you all!

08:56.520 --> 08:58.140
I'll kill you all!

09:01.840 --> 09:02.200
Dan.

09:02.630 --> 09:03.890
You want me to kill him?

09:06.670 --> 09:07.200
Mr. Bei,

09:08.600 --> 09:09.120
don't.

09:10.390 --> 09:10.960
Kill him!

09:11.360 --> 09:12.420
Why keep him alive?

09:13.080 --> 09:15.740
So he can work with Prince Duan
from the outside?

09:15.870 --> 09:17.120
I almost forgot

09:18.550 --> 09:19.950
that you're still alive.

09:24.550 --> 09:25.720
You little brat.

09:38.360 --> 09:40.910
If Prince Duan finds out that
the Yan's assassins failed,

09:40.910 --> 09:42.160
he'll go all the way

09:42.520 --> 09:44.520
and carry out the regicide himself,

09:44.910 --> 09:46.630
and he'll surely pin the blame on

09:46.630 --> 09:47.490
the Yan people.

09:49.550 --> 09:50.910
His men are already lying in ambush
in the woods.

09:50.810 --> 09:54.340
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

09:52.970 --> 09:54.480
If we confront them head-on right now,

09:54.480 --> 09:56.030
since we're badly outnumbered,

09:56.030 --> 09:58.430
I don't have absolute confidence we'd win.

09:58.910 --> 10:01.320
Yang Duojie has gone to
mobilize the Imperial Guards.

10:01.320 --> 10:02.450
The Imperial Guards

10:02.900 --> 10:04.900
might not be so easy to be mobilized.

10:05.750 --> 10:06.440
I trust him.

10:12.760 --> 10:13.420
Then let's

10:15.510 --> 10:16.330
just wait.

10:16.930 --> 10:18.990
Don't waste your energy, Xiahou Dan!

10:19.200 --> 10:22.060
We smeared the Qiang State's poison
on our weapons.

10:22.120 --> 10:23.790
Your wound won't heal.

10:24.390 --> 10:25.080
Your blood

10:25.720 --> 10:26.720
will keep flowing

10:26.910 --> 10:27.700
and flowing,

10:28.270 --> 10:29.630
until it runs dry!

10:37.030 --> 10:37.560
Someone.

10:37.910 --> 10:38.440
Someone.

10:39.820 --> 10:40.470
Someone!

10:42.120 --> 10:43.100
Who are you?

10:43.960 --> 10:44.360
Quick.

10:44.960 --> 10:46.080
I need to see Commander Zhao.

10:46.080 --> 10:47.540
Take me to Commander Zhao.

10:48.080 --> 10:50.480
You think you can see Commander Zhao
just because you want to?

10:50.480 --> 10:52.120
Send the Imperial Guards up Mount Bei.

10:52.120 --> 10:53.120
There's no time!

10:53.240 --> 10:54.370
Don't try to fool me.

10:54.600 --> 10:56.240
Commander Zhao?
What right do you have to see him?

10:56.240 --> 10:57.370
That's impossible!

10:57.390 --> 10:57.720
I really...

10:57.720 --> 10:59.450
Who's making a commotion here?

11:00.840 --> 11:01.770
Commander Zhao.

11:04.440 --> 11:05.030
Commander Zhao!

11:05.030 --> 11:07.600
Quick—lead the Imperial Guards
up Mount Bei to save His Majesty!

11:07.600 --> 11:08.130
Quick...

11:09.480 --> 11:10.340
Don't touch me.

11:14.360 --> 11:15.410
Who are you?

11:16.120 --> 11:19.600
I'm Yang Duojie, Director of
the Imperial Observatory.

11:19.760 --> 11:23.510
-Quick, save His Majesty! There's no time!
-You said you're an Imperial Astronomer?

11:23.510 --> 11:24.770
What proof do you have?

11:25.960 --> 11:26.820
I have my badge.

11:27.120 --> 11:28.120
My badge... My...

11:32.840 --> 11:34.670
I just fled for my life from Mount Bei.

11:34.670 --> 11:36.290
I must have lost it on the way.

11:36.440 --> 11:38.670
I wouldn't lie about
something this serious!

11:38.670 --> 11:40.360
I stake my life on it—

11:40.440 --> 11:41.000
every word...

11:41.000 --> 11:42.480
What use is your life to me?

11:43.320 --> 11:44.650
Look at the state of you,

11:45.240 --> 11:47.630
and you dare claim to be
from the Imperial Observatory

11:47.630 --> 11:50.160
and even try to mobilize
the Imperial Guards?

11:50.240 --> 11:50.840
Seize him!

11:52.600 --> 11:53.260
I really...

11:53.570 --> 11:53.870
I...

11:54.440 --> 11:56.550
-I'm really an Imperial Astronomer!
-Move!

11:56.550 --> 11:58.160
Save His Majesty!

11:58.840 --> 12:00.130
Commander Zhao!

12:02.200 --> 12:02.800
Lock him up

12:03.200 --> 12:04.750
and interrogate him strictly.

12:04.750 --> 12:05.680
Yes, Commander.

12:17.470 --> 12:19.070
Looks like the winds of power

12:19.680 --> 12:21.140
are really about to shift.

12:25.200 --> 12:25.790
I take my leave.

12:25.790 --> 12:26.360
I take my leave.

12:26.360 --> 12:27.360
Please take care.

12:30.240 --> 12:31.120
Lord Jia.

12:32.840 --> 12:33.480
Lord Jia.

12:36.120 --> 12:36.670
Let's

12:37.320 --> 12:39.300
raise a cup to Lord Mu from afar

12:39.720 --> 12:41.360
for this brilliant plan.

12:44.390 --> 12:47.030
Lord Mu was using that name
for the sake of staying undercover.

12:47.030 --> 12:49.220
From now on, we should use his real name

12:49.510 --> 12:50.390
and address him as

12:50.390 --> 12:52.100
Lord Murong.

12:54.960 --> 12:56.390
Everyone knows the saying,

12:56.390 --> 12:58.790
"the mantis stalks the cicada,
unaware of the oriole behind."

12:58.790 --> 12:59.850
Little do they know

12:59.870 --> 13:02.870
His Highness Prince Duan's
"bird-catcher" strategy

13:03.000 --> 13:05.050
is the truly brilliant one.

13:05.600 --> 13:09.260
The time has not yet come,
and the outcome hasn't been decided yet.

13:09.630 --> 13:12.550
Gentlemen, you should still
speak and act with caution.

13:12.550 --> 13:13.120
Yes.

13:19.480 --> 13:20.990
Stop wasting your energy.

13:20.840 --> 13:23.970
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

13:21.240 --> 13:22.790
I don't have the antidote.

13:24.080 --> 13:24.790
Xiahou Dan.

13:25.790 --> 13:28.250
I want you to savor the taste of death—

13:29.320 --> 13:31.880
just as that foolish envoy you sent did!

13:33.670 --> 13:34.680
Look at me.

13:35.790 --> 13:37.850
Do you really think he's still alive?

13:39.040 --> 13:39.780
Wang Zhao?

13:40.600 --> 13:40.970
He...

13:41.320 --> 13:42.450
He was killed.

13:43.030 --> 13:44.360
Of course he was killed!

13:45.000 --> 13:46.860
The entire real envoy delegation

13:47.000 --> 13:48.390
has been killed by me!

13:54.070 --> 13:54.730
Therefore,

13:55.030 --> 13:56.360
ending the war and establishing trade

13:55.430 --> 13:59.060
[One month ago]

13:56.630 --> 13:58.620
is not only a chance for the people
of both states

13:58.620 --> 14:00.700
to rest and recover,

14:02.120 --> 14:03.360
but for you, Emperor,

14:03.630 --> 14:05.480
it can also help strengthen state power

14:05.480 --> 14:07.010
and consolidate your rule—

14:07.080 --> 14:09.510
a win on multiple fronts.

14:13.480 --> 14:14.170
Good.

14:14.750 --> 14:15.200
Good.

14:15.670 --> 14:16.720
Wonderful.

14:19.000 --> 14:19.660
Excellent!

14:20.750 --> 14:23.020
I'm willing to send an envoy delegation

14:23.200 --> 14:26.010
to return to Great Xia with you
for peace talks.

14:26.840 --> 14:28.750
May our two states restore our friendship

14:28.750 --> 14:29.790
-Good.
-and enjoy everlasting trade.

14:29.790 --> 14:30.850
Good. This is good.

14:33.360 --> 14:34.490
This cannot be done!

14:35.750 --> 14:37.080
What are you doing here?

14:38.030 --> 14:38.800
Uncle.

14:39.750 --> 14:41.480
Have you forgotten

14:41.480 --> 14:42.940
the countless blood debts

14:44.360 --> 14:46.120
the Xia people owe our Great Yan citizens?

14:46.120 --> 14:46.860
Did Shanyi

14:47.270 --> 14:48.330
die for nothing?

14:48.790 --> 14:49.390
Nonsense!

14:50.690 --> 14:53.150
Peace talks are beneficial to
the Yan State.

14:53.200 --> 14:56.310
Prince, you should learn to
look further ahead.

14:56.840 --> 14:59.170
Don't let personal grudges and old hatred

14:59.510 --> 15:00.640
blind you.

15:01.080 --> 15:02.480
I'm speaking to my uncle.

15:03.360 --> 15:05.760
There's no place for a Qiang woman
to speak.

15:06.720 --> 15:07.200
Uncle.

15:08.420 --> 15:10.840
Could it be that you're afraid of
the Xia people?

15:10.840 --> 15:11.840
If you are afraid,

15:13.030 --> 15:14.830
I, Tu'er, am not afraid of death.

15:15.270 --> 15:17.000
I'll lead our Great Yan warriors,

15:17.000 --> 15:18.730
storm the Great Xia's capital,

15:18.790 --> 15:20.410
and take
the Great Xia Emperor's head!

15:20.410 --> 15:20.910
Shut up!

15:22.200 --> 15:22.660
Guards!

15:24.750 --> 15:26.910
Take the Prince back to his tent
to reflect on his actions.

15:26.910 --> 15:28.840
Do not let him out without my order!

15:28.840 --> 15:29.320
Yes!

15:33.720 --> 15:34.520
Just you wait,

15:35.430 --> 15:36.830
you treacherous Xia dog.

15:42.960 --> 15:43.670
Your Highness.

15:43.670 --> 15:44.510
Your Highness.

15:44.510 --> 15:45.030
Your Highness.

15:45.030 --> 15:45.890
Your Highness.

15:46.390 --> 15:46.900
Now,

15:47.120 --> 15:49.360
the peace talks have been announced
to the whole country.

15:49.360 --> 15:50.510
The envoy delegation
sent by the Emperor of Yan

15:50.510 --> 15:52.570
has already set off for the Great Xia.

15:53.440 --> 15:54.300
Your Highness.

15:55.440 --> 15:56.600
What should we do?

16:05.630 --> 16:06.960
Who among you is willing

16:07.510 --> 16:09.640
to follow me to the Great Xia's capital

16:10.200 --> 16:12.130
and chop off their Emperor's head—

16:12.840 --> 16:14.040
to make the Xia people

16:15.000 --> 16:16.370
pay with their blood?

16:22.150 --> 16:24.570
We swear to follow Prince Tu'er
to the death!

16:24.570 --> 16:27.650
We swear to follow Prince Tu'er
to the death!

16:27.910 --> 16:29.000
Kill!

16:29.390 --> 16:30.450
Protect Lord Wang!

17:02.270 --> 17:03.130
Run, Lord Wang!

18:10.350 --> 18:11.830
I will do my utmost

18:12.260 --> 18:13.960
to stop the war and establish trade.

18:13.960 --> 18:14.760
I won't return

18:16.230 --> 18:17.160
until I succeed.

18:25.340 --> 18:27.930
♪ In the time and space of chaos ♪

18:28.030 --> 18:28.550
You...

18:28.770 --> 18:31.810
♪ Every time I open my eyes ♪

18:32.500 --> 18:35.750
♪ Your silhouette is engraved inside ♪

18:38.880 --> 18:41.620
♪ Then we transform ♪

18:42.260 --> 18:45.350
♪ Into the blazing light to guard ♪

18:45.740 --> 18:50.390
♪ Our eternal galaxy ♪

18:46.240 --> 18:49.040
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

18:51.200 --> 18:53.650
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

18:54.360 --> 18:57.000
♪ And let time freeze ♪

18:56.070 --> 18:57.100
Haqina!

18:57.400 --> 18:58.660
Haqina!

18:57.700 --> 19:03.450
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

19:03.870 --> 19:05.100
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

19:05.780 --> 19:08.580
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

19:09.200 --> 19:10.810
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

19:10.850 --> 19:16.820
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

19:17.310 --> 19:18.740
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

19:18.960 --> 19:20.810
You'll surely face retribution!

19:19.290 --> 19:22.150
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

19:22.670 --> 19:24.810
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

19:22.720 --> 19:23.490
Stop moving!

19:23.750 --> 19:24.480
Stop moving.

19:24.910 --> 19:26.440
♪ We can dance together ♪

19:26.460 --> 19:36.020
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

19:28.200 --> 19:30.400
You can't afford to lose any more blood.

19:33.350 --> 19:34.750
I'm going to kill you all.

19:35.070 --> 19:36.470
I'm going to kill you all!

19:36.550 --> 19:37.440
Kill you all!

19:44.080 --> 19:46.400
Wang Zhao's mission was a secret.

19:49.750 --> 19:52.350
Even his widowed mother
didn't know the truth.

19:54.930 --> 19:55.830
I told him

19:57.010 --> 19:58.800
that the journey would be perilous,

19:58.800 --> 20:01.260
♪ Watch the universe bow ♪

20:00.720 --> 20:01.930
and that he could refuse

20:01.930 --> 20:04.620
♪ And let time freeze ♪

20:03.840 --> 20:04.930
if he wished.

20:05.320 --> 20:11.040
♪ I still gaze into those firm eyes ♪

20:08.680 --> 20:09.480
But he said...

20:09.960 --> 20:11.510
I was born on the border
between the two states.

20:11.510 --> 20:12.590
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

20:12.880 --> 20:13.680
Since childhood,

20:13.290 --> 20:16.150
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

20:14.440 --> 20:16.990
I've seen too many families
torn apart by war.

20:16.770 --> 20:18.340
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

20:17.160 --> 20:18.350
Most of my playmates

20:18.360 --> 20:24.310
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

20:19.240 --> 20:20.370
also grew up like me,

20:20.880 --> 20:22.040
unable to have

20:23.240 --> 20:24.400
both parents alive.

20:24.960 --> 20:26.240
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

20:25.760 --> 20:27.000
Some died

20:26.920 --> 20:29.730
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

20:28.590 --> 20:29.590
before even

20:30.270 --> 20:32.380
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

20:30.480 --> 20:31.680
reaching adulthood.

20:32.400 --> 20:34.040
♪ We can dance together ♪

20:33.820 --> 20:35.220
Their tiny bodies

20:34.070 --> 20:41.780
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

20:37.890 --> 20:40.090
could be wrapped in just half a reed mat.

20:44.680 --> 20:45.480
Your Majesty,

20:46.260 --> 20:48.260
peace talks are vital for our state.

20:48.590 --> 20:50.850
I'm willing to go with the resolve to die.

20:52.060 --> 20:53.240
♪ It doesn't matter ♪

20:52.640 --> 20:53.840
If anything should happen to me,

20:53.840 --> 20:56.700
♪ The world set a trap with the stars
and the moon blocking the way ♪

20:54.860 --> 20:57.320
please build a cenotaph for me,
Your Majesty,

20:57.320 --> 20:58.890
♪ I'll still stand by your side ♪

20:58.240 --> 20:59.050
so that my spirit

20:58.910 --> 21:04.890
♪ Stand like an unbreakable wall
in troubled times ♪

20:59.640 --> 21:00.570
may return home.

21:02.270 --> 21:03.470
Then this life of mine

21:04.310 --> 21:05.590
will not have been lived in vain.

21:05.590 --> 21:07.140
♪ Go to the battlefield ♪

21:07.470 --> 21:10.410
♪ Waters surge in reverse,
and time rewinds ♪

21:10.820 --> 21:12.930
♪ Sever the mundane shackles ♪

21:12.950 --> 21:14.590
♪ We can dance together ♪

21:13.830 --> 21:16.230
I must ensure
his death was not for nothing,

21:14.630 --> 21:22.390
♪ On the ruins fearlessly ♪

21:18.430 --> 21:20.830
so that his spirit in heaven
may find peace.

21:25.390 --> 21:31.370
♪ Never looking back ♪

21:29.480 --> 21:30.350
Now,

21:32.880 --> 21:33.940
let's proceed with

21:37.270 --> 21:38.200
the peace talks.

21:46.440 --> 21:48.240
What nonsense are you talking about?

21:48.240 --> 21:48.720
Wanyin,

21:51.320 --> 21:52.620
give the gun to Mr. Bei

21:53.510 --> 21:55.590
and ask him to guard the gate properly.

21:55.590 --> 21:55.960
Okay.

22:04.590 --> 22:05.320
Buddy.

22:05.590 --> 22:06.790
What's your surname?

22:09.590 --> 22:09.990
Buddy,

22:10.680 --> 22:11.410
look at this.

22:12.250 --> 22:12.780
Look.

22:17.350 --> 22:18.440
Trying to bribe me

22:18.640 --> 22:20.240
with just a few copper coins?

22:30.750 --> 22:32.410
With faith one may alter fate…

22:33.550 --> 22:34.680
Marvelous.

22:37.910 --> 22:39.510
No, no, not marvelous at all!

22:42.350 --> 22:44.720
What're you talking about,
marvelous or not?

22:44.720 --> 22:45.680
Just now,

22:46.200 --> 22:48.660
I cast a hexagram for you
using the Six Lines.

22:50.220 --> 22:53.050
There's a great calamity in your fate!

22:54.750 --> 22:56.480
If you keep spouting nonsense,

22:56.680 --> 22:58.940
I'll use the torture instruments on you.

22:59.510 --> 23:02.190
I'm the Director of
the Imperial Observatory,

23:03.000 --> 23:06.350
in charge of divining fortune
and misfortune for the royal destiny.

23:06.350 --> 23:07.070
Whether you believe my reading

23:07.070 --> 23:07.730
is up to you,

23:09.270 --> 23:11.780
and whether you can keep your new position

23:12.200 --> 23:13.510
as Deputy Commander

23:14.350 --> 23:15.400
is also up to you.

23:16.830 --> 23:17.720
How do you know

23:18.310 --> 23:20.160
I was just promoted to Deputy Commander?

23:20.160 --> 23:21.290
The will of Heaven

23:22.400 --> 23:23.530
cannot be revealed.

23:26.400 --> 23:28.280
Buddy, I wonder if you've heard

23:28.680 --> 23:29.780
the story of Cao Cao

23:30.110 --> 23:31.720
and Wang Hou?

23:32.510 --> 23:33.480
What Wang Hou?

23:33.680 --> 23:34.010
Wait,

23:34.240 --> 23:35.480
what does this have to do with me?

23:35.480 --> 23:38.400
My dear buddy,
it has everything to do with you!

23:41.790 --> 23:43.290
It is said that when Cao Cao

23:43.400 --> 23:44.640
went to conquer Yuan Shu,

23:44.640 --> 23:47.640
he encountered a drought,
and the army ran out of food.

23:47.720 --> 23:50.120
The grain officer, Wang Hou,
asked Cao Cao,

23:51.920 --> 23:53.790
"without food to eat,

23:53.880 --> 23:55.600
what should we do?"

23:58.510 --> 23:59.100
"Replace

23:59.310 --> 24:00.550
the large bushel with a smaller one

24:00.550 --> 24:03.130
when issuing the rations to them."

24:03.240 --> 24:05.690
"But the soldiers will be resentful.

24:05.750 --> 24:06.790
What then?"

24:06.790 --> 24:07.450
"No matter.

24:08.200 --> 24:10.850
I have a brilliant plan."

24:10.960 --> 24:12.480
Once the rations were reduced,

24:12.480 --> 24:14.650
the soldiers were indeed furious.

24:15.030 --> 24:16.020
And then, Cao Cao

24:16.400 --> 24:17.860
said to the grain officer,

24:19.790 --> 24:22.200
"I need to borrow one more thing from you

24:22.270 --> 24:24.030
to steady the army's morale."

24:24.240 --> 24:25.760
"What is it?"

24:26.030 --> 24:26.680
"Your

24:27.110 --> 24:29.240
head."

24:30.350 --> 24:32.910
"I am innocent! Truly innocent!"

24:33.000 --> 24:34.400
"I know you are innocent.

24:34.640 --> 24:35.250
But

24:35.440 --> 24:36.700
if I don't execute you,

24:36.920 --> 24:39.790
should I execute myself?"

24:47.240 --> 24:48.310
W-What are you talking about?

24:48.310 --> 24:49.710
Beating around the bush.

24:51.790 --> 24:52.790
Buddy,

24:53.070 --> 24:54.200
aren't you just like

24:54.730 --> 24:56.810
that Wang Hou right now?

24:59.720 --> 25:00.160
Look,

25:00.650 --> 25:03.450
Zhao Wucheng could have just
asked you to watch me.

25:03.480 --> 25:05.310
Why did he have to
order you to interrogate me

25:05.310 --> 25:06.830
in front of everyone?

25:12.920 --> 25:13.990
For failing to save His Majesty,

25:13.990 --> 25:15.570
someone's head has to roll.

25:17.590 --> 25:19.650
Even if His Majesty were to pass away,

25:19.710 --> 25:21.170
Prince Duan would still
pursue this charge

25:21.170 --> 25:22.700
to make a show of his stance.

25:23.920 --> 25:25.550
That Zhao Wucheng is Prince Duan's lackey,

25:25.550 --> 25:27.010
so of course he'll be fine.

25:27.510 --> 25:29.160
Then the one who'll be in trouble

25:29.160 --> 25:31.570
can only be whoever fails to get results
from the interrogation

25:31.570 --> 25:33.630
and delays the deployment of troops.

25:38.590 --> 25:39.850
Did you divine all this

25:40.880 --> 25:42.290
from your hexagrams?

25:44.630 --> 25:51.340
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

25:45.100 --> 25:46.640
You're a dying man,

25:47.110 --> 25:48.420
and I'm a desperado.

25:48.880 --> 25:50.550
What's there for us to talk about?

25:50.550 --> 25:52.010
Don't even think about it!

25:52.750 --> 25:53.440
Indeed.

25:54.720 --> 25:55.520
Just take it as

25:56.750 --> 25:58.110
the ramblings

25:59.680 --> 26:01.070
of a dying man.

26:02.240 --> 26:03.300
Bring him forward.

26:03.650 --> 26:08.530
[Be Remembered with Honor for All Ages]

26:11.960 --> 26:13.210
Years of war

26:14.590 --> 26:16.390
have left the people destitute.

26:17.400 --> 26:18.510
You didn't notice,

26:19.480 --> 26:20.940
but Zhaluowahan realized

26:21.920 --> 26:24.320
that the people
have lost the will to fight.

26:26.000 --> 26:27.160
He needs time

26:27.960 --> 26:29.030
to recuperate,

26:32.680 --> 26:34.610
and he also needs a new opportunity

26:35.640 --> 26:36.480
to stir up

26:37.310 --> 26:39.040
the people's fighting spirit.

26:40.680 --> 26:42.840
The Xia people know they are in the wrong,

26:42.840 --> 26:43.690
[When two states go to war,
one is bound to suffer.]

26:43.030 --> 26:45.440
so they sent someone with a peace treaty.

26:43.720 --> 26:44.440
[Prolonged war is no blessing to a state.
I seek terms with the Yan State.]

26:44.460 --> 26:45.080
[Let's set aside old grievances,
forge an alliance, and keep the peace.]

26:45.110 --> 26:45.690
[I hereby draft this pact
as a pledge of good faith and trust.]

26:46.030 --> 26:48.100
The court ministers and the people

26:48.160 --> 26:50.330
really don't want any more war.

26:50.550 --> 26:52.790
I don't want to go against
their wishes either.

26:52.790 --> 26:53.850
But Shanyi...

26:55.480 --> 26:58.480
She was our holy maiden!

27:01.880 --> 27:03.480
Shanyi was just a young girl.

27:04.590 --> 27:07.590
Why would she attempt an assassination
for no reason?

27:08.030 --> 27:08.920
Who was it

27:10.260 --> 27:11.590
that gave her the order?

27:12.920 --> 27:14.120
And how did the person

27:15.480 --> 27:17.280
who gave the order make her obey?

27:18.830 --> 27:20.030
Coercion or bribery?

27:21.280 --> 27:23.240
Or did they use her beloved

27:24.070 --> 27:25.030
to threaten her?

27:33.640 --> 27:34.640
How did Xiahou Dan

27:35.680 --> 27:37.090
know all this?

27:39.440 --> 27:41.770
Being a puppet without even realizing it—

27:43.670 --> 27:45.400
you can't save the one you love,

27:46.880 --> 27:48.920
nor can you find your true enemy.

27:51.070 --> 27:53.130
Do you really think the Emperor of Yan

27:53.580 --> 27:56.000
has no idea that you've come to
the Great Xia?

27:56.000 --> 27:57.320
Just like Shanyi,

27:58.590 --> 28:00.850
your deaths in the palace of the Great Xia

28:01.440 --> 28:04.240
would be far more useful
than dying at their hands.

28:04.480 --> 28:06.480
When the news reaches the Yan State,

28:07.880 --> 28:09.740
he can shed crocodile tears again

28:10.680 --> 28:11.270
and cry

28:13.110 --> 28:15.050
for the Xia State to pay in blood.

28:20.440 --> 28:21.240
You're right.

28:23.720 --> 28:25.130
I... I am a puppet.

28:27.330 --> 28:28.390
But what about you?

28:28.830 --> 28:29.960
Aren't you one, too?

28:30.350 --> 28:31.590
Of course I am.

28:35.160 --> 28:36.720
When I was young, I thought

28:37.570 --> 28:39.700
that if I fought with everything I had,

28:40.190 --> 28:41.960
I could escape their control.

28:43.400 --> 28:45.130
But later, I slowly realized

28:45.640 --> 28:47.100
that every decision I made

28:48.480 --> 28:50.140
and my every act of resistance

28:51.790 --> 28:53.520
played right into their hands.

28:56.750 --> 28:58.440
I am a puppet,

29:00.270 --> 29:01.510
a target,

29:03.440 --> 29:04.240
and an arrow.

29:14.590 --> 29:17.440
I am the killing blade in their hands,

29:23.750 --> 29:25.480
yet the one thing I cannot be

29:29.550 --> 29:30.210
is a person.

29:32.680 --> 29:34.140
Is what he's talking about

29:35.350 --> 29:38.350
the experience of Xiahou Dan
from the original story?

29:40.250 --> 29:42.110
Actually, we are very much alike.

29:44.110 --> 29:45.310
But I'm not resigned—

29:49.350 --> 29:51.590
I refuse to pretend to be ignorant,

29:52.720 --> 29:55.110
to drift blindly toward fate,

29:56.200 --> 29:57.570
or to deceive myself

29:58.240 --> 29:59.200
and call it

30:00.900 --> 30:02.660
"having no choice."

30:05.160 --> 30:06.160
Are you resigned?

30:09.350 --> 30:10.590
Are you?

30:17.000 --> 30:17.690
Kneel!

30:26.030 --> 30:28.440
You actually lost your composure
over a woman,

30:28.440 --> 30:30.100
ignoring the bigger picture!

30:30.640 --> 30:33.010
How can I entrust the Great Yan to you?

30:33.680 --> 30:35.340
How can you ever be an emperor?

30:35.590 --> 30:37.790
If I can't even protect the woman I love,

30:38.590 --> 30:41.310
then I'm not fit
to be the Emperor of the Yan State!

30:41.310 --> 30:42.040
You bastard!

30:45.790 --> 30:46.250
Guards!

30:46.680 --> 30:47.740
Yes, Your Majesty!

30:48.110 --> 30:49.040
Pass on my order:

30:49.550 --> 30:51.350
say that the Prince has gone mad.

30:51.720 --> 30:52.850
From this day forth,

30:53.550 --> 30:55.220
he is not to leave the camp.

30:55.720 --> 30:57.380
If he still refuses to repent,

30:57.440 --> 30:58.400
starve him!

30:58.720 --> 30:59.780
Yes, Your Majesty.

31:07.480 --> 31:08.660
I never expected

31:08.830 --> 31:11.030
that you'd be such a hopeless romantic.

31:12.920 --> 31:14.180
Since that's the case,

31:15.030 --> 31:16.290
I'll give you a poison.

31:17.790 --> 31:19.480
Smear it on a wound,

31:21.350 --> 31:23.480
and the blood will drain, ending life.

31:26.920 --> 31:28.480
Go find your Shanyi.

31:49.750 --> 31:51.070
Hate me if you want.

31:51.590 --> 31:52.880
I'm a dying man,

31:54.030 --> 31:55.360
and you're a desperado.

31:56.400 --> 31:59.000
It's just the one
who truly killed your beloved

32:01.310 --> 32:03.640
can continue to sit securely on the throne

32:04.920 --> 32:06.520
with nothing to worry about.

32:11.270 --> 32:12.200
Unfortunately,

32:13.890 --> 32:15.200
I'm about to die.

32:17.160 --> 32:20.360
If you could kill
that treacherous Emperor Zhaluowahan,

32:21.480 --> 32:23.010
it would be good news for me,

32:24.200 --> 32:25.930
and you would get your revenge.

32:26.640 --> 32:27.310
But now,

32:29.350 --> 32:31.060
you've committed regicide.

32:33.030 --> 32:35.160
You probably don't even stand a chance

32:36.670 --> 32:38.400
of leaving the Great Xia alive.

32:57.240 --> 32:59.100
I really don't have the antidote.

33:00.110 --> 33:02.170
That Qiang woman only gave me poison.

33:03.720 --> 33:05.580
Go find your imperial physicians

33:06.350 --> 33:08.150
and try to figure something out.

33:16.160 --> 33:18.370
Then please pray hard for me.

33:22.600 --> 33:24.600
Then tell me how to turn this around.

33:26.790 --> 33:27.350
Speak!

33:27.920 --> 33:31.120
To think there're people
so disrespectful of propriety—

33:31.830 --> 33:34.490
you ask for guidance
yet won't even bow to learn.

33:35.030 --> 33:36.830
I can be even more disrespectful.

33:36.830 --> 33:38.430
Are you going to speak or not?

33:41.620 --> 33:42.070
Buddy.

33:43.160 --> 33:44.690
Can you get the Tiger Tally?

33:51.030 --> 33:52.360
Greetings, Commander.

33:53.400 --> 33:54.790
How's the interrogation going?

33:54.790 --> 33:55.310
Commander,

33:55.310 --> 33:56.160
I haven't got anything out of him yet.

33:56.160 --> 33:59.090
I'll definitely
conduct a thorough interrogation.

34:17.920 --> 34:19.380
Interrogate him properly

34:19.800 --> 34:21.000
and meticulously.

34:22.510 --> 34:24.770
This is an important matter of the state.

34:26.400 --> 34:28.710
Both you and I will be credited for this.

34:30.280 --> 34:31.070
Yes, sure.

34:35.670 --> 34:37.330
Please take care, Commander.

34:57.360 --> 34:58.090
No survivor.

34:59.800 --> 35:00.260
Let's go

35:00.510 --> 35:01.440
and kill them all.

35:01.440 --> 35:01.760
Yes.

35:07.590 --> 35:09.450
I really don't have the antidote.

35:10.800 --> 35:11.190
Dan!

35:13.670 --> 35:15.070
Those ambushed in the woods

35:15.070 --> 35:15.930
have closed in.

35:18.500 --> 35:18.830
Run.

35:19.550 --> 35:20.080
Let's go.

35:20.190 --> 35:20.630
I...

35:31.880 --> 35:33.610
I don't think I can run anymore.

35:36.800 --> 35:38.200
Then let's find a place

35:38.480 --> 35:39.000
to hide

35:39.400 --> 35:39.920
and wait.

35:39.920 --> 35:40.720
Wait for what?

35:41.760 --> 35:42.810
A chance—

35:44.110 --> 35:45.310
to see whether Heaven

35:45.690 --> 35:47.340
stands on our side.

35:51.760 --> 35:53.230
Let's get in the underground palace.

35:53.230 --> 35:53.760
Let's go.

36:03.030 --> 36:04.030
What are you doing?

36:04.030 --> 36:04.720
Let go of me!

36:28.400 --> 36:29.640
I will lure them away

36:29.800 --> 36:31.610
to buy Your Majesty some time.

36:46.920 --> 36:47.380
Wanyin.

36:55.070 --> 36:56.470
This underground palace

36:56.510 --> 36:58.070
is like a shelter.

36:59.840 --> 37:01.970
Its locking stone falls into a groove,

37:03.630 --> 37:05.370
forming a triangle

37:05.710 --> 37:07.480
with the stone gate and the ground.

37:07.480 --> 37:08.810
Without special tools,

37:09.480 --> 37:11.410
it's hard to open with brute force.

37:11.920 --> 37:12.710
This is

37:14.360 --> 37:15.960
the stability of a triangle.

37:17.320 --> 37:18.360
Not bad, CEO Dan.

37:18.800 --> 37:20.000
You still remember what you learned

37:20.000 --> 37:21.260
back in middle school.

37:22.280 --> 37:23.230
After all, it is

37:23.840 --> 37:26.100
the crystallization of ancient wisdom.

37:46.280 --> 37:46.830
Lord Cao.

37:47.110 --> 37:48.960
We didn't find the bodies of
His Majesty and Tu'er.

37:48.960 --> 37:50.590
Keep searching. They won't get far.

37:50.590 --> 37:50.970
Yes.

37:51.710 --> 37:52.240
Found it!

37:52.280 --> 37:52.810
Found it!

37:53.550 --> 37:54.760
There is blood
near the underground palace.

37:54.760 --> 37:55.760
They must be hiding there.

37:55.760 --> 37:57.370
What are you waiting for? Go!

38:11.270 --> 38:11.940
My Lord.

38:12.110 --> 38:12.850
The gate is blocked from inside.

38:12.850 --> 38:14.380
His Majesty must be inside.

38:17.510 --> 38:18.640
Break the gate down.

38:44.360 --> 38:45.550
Harder!

38:47.510 --> 38:48.910
Bring the battering ram!

38:50.000 --> 38:50.550
Yes!
